{"tid":686314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【另類葬禮】私家車當棺材吊落墳 網民：盜墓賊正趕來","createTime":"2018-06-01T06:53:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-01T08:25:48.000Z","uid":13468,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0dd517b61e510745054bdcf5b9f139149da92e35","tid":686314,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T06:53:37.000Z","msg":"【另類葬禮】私家車當棺材吊落墳 網民：盜墓賊正趕來<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180531/large/1527768603_b052.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180531%2Flarge%2F1527768603_b052.jpg&h=c9834151&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國殯葬傳統，一般人都會用上棺材，讓逝者入土為安。河北保定市近日卻有一個與別不同的葬禮，家屬竟用轎車代替棺材。<br />\n<br />\n事發於星期一（5月28日），河北保定一村民離世後，家人用轎車當棺材下葬。當地村民說，死者生前喜歡車，立下遺囑，要下葬時，把其骨灰盒放車內，再將轎車當棺材埋入墳墓內。有指汽車車齡頗大，僅值萬多元人民幣而已。<br />\n<br />\n葬禮影片在網上熱傳，見一輛銀色私家車被吊入土坑。無數網民即時留言，有人調侃「幸好死者不喜歡航空母艦」，亦有人擔心會有盜墓賊。<br />\n<br />\n網民留言：<br />\n冷冷的淡然：幸好不是超喜歡航空母艦<br />\n蒼老師結婚了啊：三天後車去人留坑<br />\n屁股很大OK：污染環境，破壞耕地<br />\n江子鴨：一大波盜墓賊正在趕來。<br />\n維維香奶：土豪啊<br />\n啊震同學：車葬！<br />\necho-nic：這也太為難未來的考古工作者了<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180601/58261710\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180601%2F58261710&d=JnLVKeEM%2FheA9YYMrJKQb%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=e12827a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180601%2F58261710&h=d8e66062\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180601/58261710</a>"},{"pid":"d3c4cefbb35430cbb7b7ccf92863c70216f87659","tid":686314,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T06:56:07.000Z","msg":"黐線附近一定好大陣屍臭味"},{"pid":"9a677c4dd49c6658da402f60fb020f27b35f6c4d","tid":686314,"uid":8636,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"d3c4cefbb35430cbb7b7ccf92863c70216f87659"